>
<!ELEMENT grouplist (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT hash (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT home (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT inact (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT last_change (#PCDATA)>
